title: WILD ENDING: Deandre Ayton Dunks Game-Winner After Paul George Misses Two Free Throws
author: Bleacher Report
description:
Monty Williams drew up the perfect play for Deandre Ayton as the Phoenix Suns escaped Game 2 with a wild game-winning lob to take a 2-0 series lead.
